locality: Kibwele Estate, Brooke Bond Tanzania; at swampy edge of lake above dam on Luisenga Stream at Mufindi Rod and Gun Club fishing lodge.
Iringa: Mufindi District. Burned grassland and wet meadow at Itimbo.
Plants of the Manovo-Gounda-St. Floris National Park. WWF Inter. Elephant Cons. Project. Along E side of Koumbala River just S of Camp Koumbala. 8º29'N, 21º13'E. Elev. 585 m; prec. 1200 mm.
Ci: Bord de Bowal de Toumodi Nord
A 45 Km au SE de Linté, près Mankim (route Ntui - Yoko)
Likouala Department: Close to the edge of Nsassa Forest, 2 km W of Epena. Lac Télé Community Reserve.
